@startuml Deployment_04_BuildPipeline

title Deployment-Diagramm Teil 4 - Build & Deployment Pipeline

package "Entwicklung" {
    artifact "Source Code" as SRC {
        component "Java Files" as JAVA
        component "JSP Files" as JSP_FILES
        component "CSS/JS Files" as ASSETS
    }
    
    artifact "Git Repository" as GIT {
        component "Main Branch" as MAIN
        component "Feature Branches" as FEATURES
    }
}

package "Build Prozess" {
    artifact "Maven" as MAVEN {
        component "pom.xml" as POM
        component "Compile Phase" as COMPILE
        component "Test Phase" as TEST
        component "Package Phase" as PACKAGE
    }
}

package "Build Artifacts" {
    artifact "Target Directory" as TARGET {
        component "wissentest.war" as WAR_FILE
        component "test-results" as TEST_RESULTS
    }
}

package "Deployment" {
    node "Tomcat Server" as TOMCAT_DEPLOY {
        artifact "webapps/" as WEBAPPS {
            component "wiskentest/" as CONTEXT
        }
    }
}

package "Runtime" {
    node "JVM Instance" as JVM {
        component "ClassLoader" as LOADER
        component "Thread Pool" as THREADS
        component "Memory Heap" as HEAP
    }
}

package "Datenbank" {
    node "PostgreSQL" as PG {
        database "wissentest DB" as PG_DB
    }
}

' Workflow
SRC --> GIT : "Push"
GIT --> MAVEN : "Maven Build"

MAVEN --> COMPILE : "Kompilierung"
COMPILE --> TEST : "Unit Tests"
TEST --> PACKAGE : "Package WAR"
PACKAGE --> TARGET : "Erstellt WAR"

TARGET --> TOMCAT_DEPLOY : "Auto-Deploy\n(CATALINA_HOME/webapps)"
TOMCAT_DEPLOY --> JVM : "JVM startet"
JVM --> PG : "JDBC Connections"

note right of SRC
  **Source Code Struktur:**
  
  src/main/java/
    - Servlets
    - Services
    - DAOs
    - Models
  
  src/main/webapp/
    - JSP Files
    - CSS/JS
    - WEB-INF/web.xml
  
  src/test/java/
    - JUnit Tests
end note

note right of MAVEN
  **Maven Build Lifecycle:**
  
  1. Validate
  2. Compile
  3. Test (JUnit)
  4. Package (WAR)
  5. Verify
  6. Install
  7. Deploy
  
  **Abhängigkeiten:**
  - Servlet API
  - PostgreSQL Driver
  - JUnit 5
  - HikariCP
end note

note right of TARGET
  **Build Output:**
  
  wissentest.war
  - Alle kompilierten Classes
  - JAR Abhängigkeiten
  - JSP Files
  - Static Assets
  - web.xml Deployment Descriptor
  
  Größe: ~50-100 MB
end note

note right of TOMCAT_DEPLOY
  **Tomcat Auto-Deploy:**
  
  1. WAR in webapps/ kopieren
  2. Tomcat erkennt Datei
  3. Unpacks wissentest.war
  4. Erstellt /wiskentest/ Verzeichnis
  5. Lädt Klassen über ClassLoader
  6. Application ist verfügbar
end note

note right of JVM
  **JVM Konfiguration:**
  
  JAVA_OPTS="-Xms256m -Xmx512m"
  
  - Min Heap: 256 MB
  - Max Heap: 512 MB
  - GC: Default (G1GC)
  - Threads: Pool für Requests
end note

note bottom
  **Gesamter Deployment-Flow:**
  
  Code → Git → Maven Build → WAR
  → Tomcat Auto-Deploy → JVM
  → Datenbank Verbindung
  → Application Live!
end note

@enduml
